    <h1 class="hero-h">Best <em style="color:#00C853;font-style:italic;">AI voice platforms</em> and voice agents</h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">Vapi, Retell, Bland, Synthflow, ElevenLabs, and PolyAI all let you build AI voice agents that answer or place real phone calls, but they are built for very different people. The real split is between developer platforms you assemble, no-code builders you click together, and managed enterprise services someone else runs for you. Pick the wrong side of that line and you either ship nothing because you needed engineers, or you overpay an enterprise vendor for a job a no-code agent could do in an afternoon.</p>
  </div>
